imdb.plot outline: A weekly television series featuring a mix of celebrity interviews, getaway travel, healthy cooking, fitness, beauty, fashion, and lifestyle segments with Host, Patrick Dockry. This 13 episode, ½-hour, weekly lifestyle series promotes positive, healthy lifestyles with a stylish twist, and explores trends in lifestyle, food, beauty & fashion, health & fitness, travel, celebrity, and non-profit organizations.
